{"Title":"盐菜蒸腊肉的做法","Primary":["梅菜150克","腊肉200克"],"Auxiliary":["食盐1/2茶匙","生抽1茶匙","蚝油1/2茶匙","剁椒1汤匙","蒜1/2头"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.腊肉和梅菜都洗干净","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_32148.jpg","2.把洗净的腊肉切片，不要太过薄","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_10374.jpg","3.然后摆入碗中","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_05185.jpg","4.再把洗净的梅菜放入腊肉中","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_33646.jpg","5.洒上食盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_80797.jpg","6.放入生抽","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_85620.jpg","7.放上剁碎的蒜末","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_19047.jpg","8.再放上一些剁椒","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_06831.jpg","9.入蒸锅","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_66423.jpg","10.蒸制20分钟即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_21205.jpg","11.倒扣入碗中，可以上桌啦","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_82176.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_70095.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/203/113291/n113291_16160.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/203/113291/n113291_00486.jpg","烹饪技巧","1、梅菜吃的就是干香，所以稍稍冲下水即可，不要久泡，以免味道都冲淡了；2、腊肉已经有咸味，并且剁辣椒也是咸的，所以再放其它调味料一定要慎重。"]}